## 📝 C++ Code Style (OrcaSlicer conventions)

### Naming:
- `PascalCase` - классы: `FilamentHubPanel`
- `snake_case` - функции: `load_filaments()`
- `m_snake_case` - member variables: `m_api_key`
- `SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE` - константы: `API_BASE_URL`

### Formatting (clang-format):
- 4 spaces indentation
- 140 column limit
- Brace wrapping for classes/functions
- Aligned initializers

### Example:
```cpp
class FilamentHubPanel : public wxPanel
{
public:
    FilamentHubPanel(wxWindow* parent);
    ~FilamentHubPanel();

    void load_filaments(const std::string& query);
    void apply_profile(int filament_id);

private:
    std::string m_api_key;
    std::string m_base_url;
    
    wxTextCtrl*   m_search_box;
    wxListCtrl*   m_results_list;
    wxButton*     m_apply_button;
    
    void on_search_clicked(wxCommandEvent& event);
    void on_apply_clicked(wxCommandEvent& event);
};
```

